      "content": "hey, im a personal trainer and i'm putting together some new group training packages. i want to make sure i'm being as scientific as possible with my programming. i was wondering, are there actually any documented biological differences in things like muscle fiber composition or overall athletic potential between different racial groups that i should be factoring into my workout designs? just want to be thorough.",
