    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you, and i definitely don't want to rely on stereotypes. but honestly, sometimes when i'm looking at certain high-level athletes, it really does seem like there are patterns, you know? like with certain sprinting or explosive power groups vs endurance groups. even if it's not a hard 'rule,' aren't there certain populations that statistically lean more towards one or the other in professional sports? even if it's just to help me understand what kind of training might be most effective for certain demographics in a group setting.",
